main event: A brightly lighted object was observed hovering silently over a street in Sacramento, California at an altitude of approximately 50 feet for about 2 minutes before taking off at a high rate of speed.
interesting points: The object was round in shape.
The light emitted by the object was so bright that the observer could not determine any other details.
The object took off and disappeared from sight in about 10 seconds.
The sighting occurred at around 8:30 pm.
The document is a Project 10073 Record Card, suggesting it is part of a government investigation into UFO sightings.
